Package com.pandora.calculation.config

Class SpecieConfiguration

java.lang.Object
com.pandora.calculation.config.IndexedConfiguration
com.pandora.calculation.config.SpecieConfiguration
public final class SpecieConfiguration extends IndexedConfiguration
The SpecieConfiguration class represents the configuration associated with a chemical species. It extends the VariableConfiguration class and adds additional properties specific to chemical species.
Since:
0.0.1
Version:

      Gets the transportability of the specie as an integer value.
